{
  "stem": "7157.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Incidentally, it's the city where my brother was born, also, in Bielsko.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was from Wroclaw.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But we went back to Bielsko and went to our apartments, the apartment building we had there, and lived there, got an apartment and lived there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was probably already after the war was over-- literally over, not just for us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In other words, the Russians had already taken Berlin, and the war was over.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So we're now talking '45-- mid-'45.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we started-- Wujek started trading, making some money, and things happened that way.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was, of course, taken by the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were being paid, but certainly not to us-- to the city administration and what have you.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We paid rent when we moved-- when we were there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In fact, kind of the incident, you might say, that got me to the United States was-- George and I went to a movie, our first movie.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is now 1945.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm 10 years old, and he's 12.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we left the movie, we were going back towards our place, and some kids started screaming at us-- 'Jews, Jews!' Now these are the Polish kids. 'Jews!' And they started throwing stones at us.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we came-- we ran home, of course, and told my mother this.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother said, OK, that's it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're leaving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because Wujek really wanted to stay in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, his sister was there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He knew the language.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He knew how to do business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She said no, we're leaving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he wanted to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She wanted to go to USA.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Basically, she said, you want to go to Israel, you go to Israel, because I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We're finished struggling.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We're going to America.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We actually went from Poland to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
